{"type":"message","id":"142abdf6","parentId":"9b527d4f","timestamp":"2026-03-23T01:19:01.057Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"所有文件都存在！现在设置 API key 并验证运行时。但等等，PowerShell 中的环境变量设置只在当前会话有效，而后续的 exec 命令会在新的进程中运行。\n\n我需要通过 exec 的 env 参数传递环境变量。让我直接在运行 CLI 时传递环境变量。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"所有文件已下载 ✓\n\n**步骤 4：设置 API key 并验证运行时**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_274184abfa154949a3357f16","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\skills\\qveris-official\\scripts\\qveris_tool.mjs\" --help","env":{"QVERIS_API_KEY":"sk-hMO0d_9xg4xdl7b4WdGtbd4ASwuk-ra2SgDXka4Vrk8"}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":16,"output":235,"cacheRead":19688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19939,"cost":{"input":0.0000096,"output":0.000517,"cacheRead":0.00216568,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00269228}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774228722333}}
{"type":"message","id":"ce8a9693","parentId":"142abdf6","timestamp":"2026-03-23T01:19:02.929Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_274184abfa154949a3357f16","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"QVeris Capability Discovery & Tool Calling CLI\n\nUsage:\n  node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs discover <query> [options]\n  node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs call <tool_id> --discovery-id <id> [options]\n  node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs inspect <tool_id> [tool_id2 ...] [options]\n\nCommands:\n  discover <query>            Discover tool candidates for a capability description\n  call <tool_id>              Call the selected tool through QVeris\n  inspect <id> [id2 ...]      Inspect tool details before reuse or calling\n\nNotes:\n  discover returns tool candidates and metadata, not final data results\n  call returns the execution result\n  all requests are routed to https://qveris.ai/api/v1\n\nOptions:\n  --limit N          Max results for discover (default: 10)\n  --discovery-id ID  Discovery ID from previous discover (required for call, optional for inspect)\n  --params JSON      Tool parameters as JSON string (default: \"{}\")\n  --max-size N       Max response size in bytes (default: 20480)\n  --timeout N        Request timeout in seconds (default: 30 for discover/inspect, 60 for call)\n  --json             Output raw JSON instead of formatted display\n  --help             Show this help message\n\nExamples:\n  node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs discover \"weather forecast API\"\n  node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs call openweathermap.weather.execute.v1 --discovery-id abc123 --params '{\"city\": \"London\"}'\n  node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs inspect openweathermap.weather.execute.v1"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1869,"aggregated":"QVeris Capability Discovery & Tool Calling CLI\n\nUsage:\n  node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs discover <query> [options]\n  node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs call <tool_id> --discovery-id <id> [options]\n  node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs inspect <tool_id> [tool_id2 ...] [options]\n\nCommands:\n  discover <query>            Discover tool candidates for a capability description\n  call <tool_id>              Call the selected tool through QVeris\n  inspect <id> [id2 ...]      Inspect tool details before reuse or calling\n\nNotes:\n  discover returns tool candidates and metadata, not final data results\n  call returns the execution result\n  all requests are routed to https://qveris.ai/api/v1\n\nOptions:\n  --limit N          Max results for discover (default: 10)\n  --discovery-id ID  Discovery ID from previous discover (required for call, optional for inspect)\n  --params JSON      Tool parameters as JSON string (default: \"{}\")\n  --max-size N       Max response size in bytes (default: 20480)\n  --timeout N        Request timeout in seconds (default: 30 for discover/inspect, 60 for call)\n  --json             Output raw JSON instead of formatted display\n  --help             Show this help message\n\nExamples:\n  node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs discover \"weather forecast API\"\n  node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs call openweathermap.weather.execute.v1 --discovery-id abc123 --params '{\"city\": \"London\"}'\n  node scripts/qveris_tool.mjs inspect openweathermap.weather.execute.v1","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774228742927}}
