{"type":"message","id":"4f625b01","parentId":"76ed8f40","timestamp":"2026-03-23T02:47:27.334Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个命令也在运行。看起来系统中有很多Python进程在执行。我应该等待它们完成，或者检查是否有错误。\n\n让我直接尝试查看控制台输出或日志。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"命令正在执行中...让我尝试简化扫描测试："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b8060e92aa8a42a0b102d8db","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\test_scan.py","content":"import akshare as ak\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\nprint(\"测试akshare连接...\")\n\ntry:\n    # 获取主板股票列表\n    stocks = ak.stock_info_a_code_name()\n    print(f\"Total stocks: {len(stocks)}\")\n\n    # 筛选主板非ST\n    main_board = []\n    for idx, row in stocks.iterrows():\n        code = row['code']\n        name = row['name']\n        if code.startswith('60') or code.startswith('00'):\n            if 'ST' not in name and '*ST' not in name:\n                main_board.append(code)\n        if len(main_board) >= 5:  # 只取前5个测试\n            break\n\n    print(f\"Main board non-ST stocks (first 5): {main_board}\")\n\n    # 获取历史数据测试\n    if main_board:\n        test_code = main_board[0]\n        end_date = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n        start_date = (datetime.now() - timedelta(days=120)).strftime('%Y%m%d')\n\n        print(f\"\\nTesting data fetch for {test_code}...\")\n        df = ak.stock_zh_a_hist(symbol=test_code, period=\"daily\",\n                                   start_date=start_date, end_date=end_date,\n                                   adjust=\"qfq\")\n        print(f\"Data points: {len(df)}\")\n        print(f\"Columns: {df.columns.tolist()}\")\n        print(f\"Last 5 rows:\\n{df.tail()}\")\n\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"Error: {e}\")\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":137213,"output":429,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137642,"cost":{"input":0.08232779999999999,"output":0.0009438000000000001,"c