{"type":"message","id":"b46eb7e9","parentId":"e2f2b146","timestamp":"2026-03-23T02:55:17.429Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Python进程已终止。现在让我分析为什么没有找到候选股票，并提供解决方案。我应该：\n\n1. 解释可能的原因（数据延迟、策略条件过严格、技术指标计算问题）\n2. 提供调试建议\n3. 提供简化版的扫描用于测试\n\n让我提供一个诊断方案和修复建议。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已停止扫描进程。## 📊 扫描结果诊断\n\n### 扫描结果\n- **scan_results.csv**：5字节（空文件）\n- **scan_results.json**：`[]`（空数组）\n\n### 可能的原因\n\n1. **数据延迟** ⚠️\n   - akshare获取的历史数据可能有1-2天延迟\n   - 2026年3月23日的数据可能不完整\n   - 无法计算准确的MA5、MA10均线\n\n2. **策略条件过严** ⚠️\n   - 同时满足\"金叉+成交量放大1.5倍+RSI<70\"的股票可能很少\n   - 市场震荡期，符合条件的股票确实很少\n\n3. **技术指标计算错误** ⚠️\n   - 数据格式不一致\n   - 计算逻辑有问题\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 调试方案\n\n### 方案1：放宽条件快速测试"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_caa5432cca054f199cfa48fc","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import akshare as ak\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\nprint(\"诊断扫描：放宽条件测试...\")\n\ntry:\n    # 获取主板股票\n    stocks = ak.stock_info_a_code_name()\n    print(f\"Total stocks: {len(stocks)}\")\n\n    # 筛选主板\n    main_board = []\n    for idx, row in stocks.iterrows():\n        code = row['code']\n        name = row['name']\n        if code.startswith('60') or code.startswith('00'):\n            if 'ST' not in name and '*ST' not in name:\n                main_board.append(code)\n        if len(main_board) >= 50:  # 只取前50个测试\n            break\n\n    print(f\"Main board stocks (test 50): {len(main_board)}\")\n\n    # 测试每只股票\n    results = []\n    for code in main_board:\n        try:\n            # 获取数据\n            end_date = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n            start_date = (datetime.now() - timedelta(days=120)).strftime('%Y%m%d')\n\n            df = ak.stock_zh_a_hist(symbol=code, period=\"daily\",\n                                       start_date=start_date, end_date=end_date,\n                                       adjust=\"qfq\")\n\n            if len(df) < 20:\n                continue\n\n            # 计算指标\n            df['MA5'] = df['close'].rolling(window=5).mean()\n            df['MA10'] = df['close'].rolling(window=10).mean()\n\n            latest = df.iloc[-1]\n            prev = df.iloc[-2]\n\n            # 检查金叉\n            ma5_golden = (prev['MA5'] < prev['MA10']) and (latest['MA5'] > latest['MA10'])\n\n            # 计算成交量比\n            avg_vol = df['volume'].iloc[-20:].mean()\n            vol_ratio = latest['volume'] / avg_vol if avg_vol > 0 else 0\n\n            # 计算RSI\n            delta = df['close'].diff()\n            gain = (delta.where(delta > 0, 0)).rolling(window=14).mean()\n            loss = (-delta.where(delta < 0, 0)).rolling(window=14).mean()\n            rs = gain / loss\n            rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + rs))\n\n            results.append({\n                'code': code,\n                'close': latest['close'],\n                'change': latest.get('pct_chg', 0) * 100,\n                'ma5_golden': ma5_golden,\n                'vol_ratio': vol_ratio,\n                'rsi': rsi.iloc[-1] if not pd.isna(rsi.iloc[-1]) else 0,\n                'name': ''\n            })\n\n        except Exception as e:\n            results.append({\n                'code': code,\n                'error': str(e),\n                'ma5_golden': False,\n                'vol_ratio': 0,\n                'rsi': 0\n            })\n            continue\n\n    # 显示结果\n    print(\"\\n扫描结果（前50只主板股）：\")\n    print(\"=\"*80)\n    print(f\"{'代码':<10} {'现价':<10} {'涨跌幅':<10} {'金叉':<8} {'量比':<10} {'RSI':<10}\")\n    print(\"-\"*80)\n\n    golden_count = 0\n    vol_enough_count = 0\n    rsi_ok_count = 0\n\n    for r in results:\n        if 'error' in r:\n            print(f\"{r['code']:<10} 错误: {r['error']}\")\n        else:\n            golden = \"是\" if r['ma5_golden'] else \"否\"\n            vol = \"是\" if r['vol_ratio'] >= 1.5 else \"否\"\n            rsi_ok = \"是\" if r['rsi'] < 70 else \"否\"\n\n            if r['ma5_golden']:\n                golden_count += 1\n            if r['vol_ratio'] >= 1.5:\n                vol_enough_count += 1\n            if r['rsi'] < 70:\n                rsi_ok_count += 1\n\n            print(f\"{r['code']:<10} {r['close']:<10.2f} {r['change']:>8.2f}% {golden:<8} {vol:>6.1f} {rsi_ok:<10}\")\n\n    print(\"\\n统计：\")\n    print(f\"出现金叉的股票：{golden_count}\")\n    print(f\"成交量≥1.5倍的股票：{vol_enough_count}\")\n    print(f\"RSI<70的股票：{rsi_ok_count}\")\n    print(f\"同时满足金叉+量比+RSI的股票：待筛选\")\n\n    # 保存诊断结果\n    df = pd.DataFrame([r for r in results if 'error' not in r])\n    df.to_csv('diagnostic_results.csv', index=False, encoding='utf-8-sig')\n    print(\"\\n诊断结果已保存到：diagnostic_results.csv\")\n\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"诊断失败：{e}\")\n","path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\diagnostic_scan.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":137213,"output":1471,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138684,"cost":{"input":0.08232779999999999,"output":0.0032362000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.08556399999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774234418413}}
