{"type":"message","id":"0b0b5ced","parentId":"3e5ea85a","timestamp":"2026-03-23T03:05:58.071Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看到所有CSV文件都是5字节，说明确实是空的。这说明扫描脚本确实运行了，但没有找到符合条件的股票，或者数据获取有问题。\n\n现在我需要：\n1. 告知用户当前情况\n2. 提供解决方案\n\n可能的问题：\n1. akshare API问题 - 数据源可能没有返回数据或格式不对\n2. 数据延迟 - 2026年3月23日的数据可能不完整（未来日期）\n3. 策略条件太严 - 确实没有股票同时满足三个条件\n4. Windows编码问题导致文件保存失败\n\n建议：\n1. 使用实际历史日期测试（如使用2026年3月20日的数据）\n2. 更换数据源（如使用tushare）\n3. 放宽条件（只看金叉或只看放量）","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 扫描结果汇总\n\n### 当前状态\n所有扫描结果文件都是**空文件**（5字节），说明：\n- ✅ 脚本已执行\n- ❌ 没有找到符合条件的候选股票\n\n### 生成的文件\n| 文件 | 大小 | 内容 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `scan_results.csv` | 5字节 | 空 |\n| `scan_results.json` | 2字节 | `[]` |\n| `test_results_relaxed.csv` | 5字节 | 空 |\n| `diagnostic_results.csv` | 5字节 | 空 |\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 可能的原因分析\n\n### 1. 数据延迟 ⚠️ **最可能**\n- **当前日期**：2026年3月23日（周末）\n- **交易日**：A股周五收盘（3月21日）\n- **问题**：akshare可能没有3月23日（非交易日）的完整数据\n- **结果**：无法准确计算MA5、MA10均线\n\n### 2. 策略条件过严\n- 同时满足\"金叉+放量1.5倍+RSI<70\"的股票确实很少\n- 市场震荡期，符合三条件的股票接近0\n\n### 3. akshare API问题\n- 网络连接不稳定\n- API返回数据格式不符合预期\n- 编码问题导致处理失败\n\n---\n\n## 💡 解决方案\n\n### 方案1：使用历史日期测试（推荐）"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1b9e30b927904737a69d4582","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import akshare as ak\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\nprint(\"使用历史日期测试（2026-03-20）...\")\n\ntry:\n    # 使用历史交易日\n    end_date = \"20260320\"\n    start_date = \"20260101\"\n\n    print(f\"数据时间范围：{start_date} ~ {end_date}\")\n\n    # 获取主板股票\n    stocks = ak.stock_info_a_code_name()\n    main_board = []\n\n    for idx, row in stocks.iterrows():\n        code = row['code']\n        name = row['name']\n        if code.startswith('60') or code.startswith('00'):\n            if 'ST' not in name and '*ST' not in name:\n                main_board.append({'code': code, 'name': name})\n\n    print(f\"主板非ST股票：{len(main_board)}\")\n\n    # 扫描前30只股票\n    candidates = []\n    for i, stock in enumerate(main_board[:30]):\n        code = stock['code']\n\n        try:\n            df = ak.stock_zh_a_hist(symbol=code, period=\"daily\",\n                                       start_date=start_date, end_date=end_date,\n                                       adjust=\"qfq\")\n\n            if len(df) < 20:\n                continue\n\n            df['MA5'] = df['close'].rolling(window=5).mean()\n            df['MA10'] = df['close'].rolling(window=10).mean()\n            df['AvgVolume'] = df['volume'].rolling(window=20).mean()\n            df['VolumeRatio'] = df['volume'] / df['AvgVolume']\n\n            latest = df.iloc[-1]\n            prev = df.iloc[-2]\n\n            # 金叉\n            ma5_golden = (prev['MA5'] < prev['MA10']) and (latest['MA5'] > latest['MA10'])\n            if not ma5_golden:\n                continue\n\n            # 成交量\n            if latest['VolumeRatio'] < 1.5:\n                continue\n\n            # RSI\n            delta = df['close'].diff()\n            gain = (delta.where(delta > 0, 0)).rolling(window=14).mean()\n            loss = (-delta.where(delta < 0, 0)).rolling(window=14).mean()\n            rs = gain / loss\n            rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + rs))\n\n            if pd.isna(rsi.iloc[-1]) or rsi.iloc[-1] >= 70:\n                continue\n\n            candidates.append({\n                'code': code,\n                'name': stock['name'],\n                'close': latest['close'],\n                'date': latest['日期'],\n                'ma5': latest['MA5'],\n                'ma10': latest['MA10'],\n                'volume_ratio': latest['VolumeRatio'],\n                'rsi': rsi.iloc[-1]\n            })\n\n            print(f\"找到候选：{code} {stock['name']}\")\n\n        except Exception as e:\n            continue\n\n    if candidates:\n        df = pd.DataFrame(candidates)\n        df.to_csv('historical_scan_results.csv', index=False, encoding='utf-8-sig')\n        print(f\"\\n找到 {len(candidates)} 个候选，已保存到：historical_scan_results.csv\")\n    else:\n        print(\"\\n未找到符合条件的候选股票\")\n\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"错误：{e}\")\n","path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\test_historical_date.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":125780,"output":1401,"cacheRead":5912,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133093,"cost":{"input":0.075468,"output":0.0030822000000000002,"cacheRead":0.00065032,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.07920051999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774235114359}}
