{"type":"message","id":"816bd3fa","parentId":"ae30cc83","timestamp":"2026-03-23T04:36:38.006Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的！有输出数据了。akshare能够获取股票列表和数据。但是获取历史数据的部分卡住了（只显示到\"数据日期范围\"）。这可能是因为：\n1. 数据量太大\n2. akshare服务器响应慢\n3. 网络问题\n\n让我创建一个使用更短日期范围的测试。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 测试结果分析\n\n从输出文件看到：\n\n### ✅ 成功的部分\n1. **获取股票列表**：5,491只股票\n2. **主板股票**：3,194只\n3. **主板非ST股票**：3,065只\n4. **数据获取开始**：正在获取平安银行（000001）的历史数据\n\n### ⚠️ 卡住的部分\n- **历史数据获取**：在\"数据日期范围\"之后没有继续输出\n- **可能原因**：\n  1. akshare API响应慢（120天数据量较大）\n  2. 网络连接不稳定\n  3. 数据日期是历史数据（2026-01-01~2026-03-20），可能服务器处理慢\n\n---\n\n## 💡 优化建议\n\n### 方案1：使用更短日期范围"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a6b2a345e3854cda8ebe63d7","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\n使用较短日期范围的akshare测试（最近30天）\n\"\"\"\nimport akshare as ak\nimport sys\n\noutput_file = open('akshare_short_test.txt', 'w', encoding='utf-8')\n\ndef log(msg):\n    print(msg)\n    output_file.write(msg + '\\n')\n    output_file.flush()\n\ntry:\n    from datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\n    log(\"=\"*60)\n    log(\"使用短期日期测试（最近30天）\")\n    log(\"=\"*60)\n\n    # 获取主板非ST股票\n    stocks = ak.stock_info_a_code_name()\n    main_board = stocks[\n        (stocks['code'].str.startswith('60') | stocks['code'].str.startswith('00'))\n    ]\n    non_st = main_board[\n        (~main_board['name'].str.contains('ST'))\n    ]\n\n    log(f\"主板非ST股票: {len(non_st)}\")\n\n    # 测试获取历史数据（最近30天）\n    test_code = non_st.iloc[0]['code']\n    test_name = non_st.iloc[0]['name']\n\n    log(f\"\\n测试股票: {test_code} ({test_name})\")\n\n    # 只获取最近30天数据\n    end_date = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n    start_date = (datetime.now() - timedelta(days=30)).strftime('%Y%m%d')\n\n    log(f\"数据日期范围: {start_date} ~ {end_date}（30天）\")\n\n    df = ak.stock_zh_a_hist(\n        symbol=test_code,\n        period=\"daily\",\n        start_date=start_date,\n        end_date=end_date,\n        adjust=\"qfq\"\n    )\n\n    log(f\"数据点数: {len(df)}\")\n\n    # 计算指标\n    df['MA5'] = df['close'].rolling(window=5).mean()\n    df['MA10'] = df['close'].rolling(window=10).mean()\n    df['AvgVolume'] = df['volume'].rolling(window=20).mean()\n    df['VolumeRatio'] = df['volume'] / df['AvgVolume']\n\n    latest = df.iloc[-1]\n    prev = df.iloc[-2]\n\n    log(f\"\\n最后交易日: {latest['日期']}\")\n    log(f\"收盘价: {latest['close']:.2f}\")\n    log(f\"MA5: {latest['MA5']:.2f}\")\n    log(f\"MA10: {latest['MA10']:.2f}\")\n\n    golden_cross = (prev['MA5'] < prev['MA10']) and (latest['MA5'] > latest['MA10'])\n    vol_ratio = latest['VolumeRatio']\n\n    log(f\"\\n技术指标:\")\n    log(f\"金叉: {'是' if golden_cross else '否'}\")\n    log(f\"成交量比: {vol_ratio:.2f}倍\")\n\n    if golden_cross and vol_ratio >= 1.5:\n        log(\"\\n✅ 符合金叉+放量条件！\")\n    else:\n        log(\"\\n❌ 不符合条件\")\n\n    log(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*60)\n    log(\"测试完成！\")\n\nexcept Exception as e:\n    log(f\"错误: {e}\")\n    import traceback\n    traceback.print_exc()\nfinally:\n    output_file.close()\n","path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\short_range_test.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":112,"output":1035,"cacheRead":122755,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123902,"cost":{"input":0.0000672,"output":0.002277,"cacheRead":0.01350305,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01584725}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774240562892}}
