{"type":"message","id":"3bd6a70b","parentId":"039e7a20","timestamp":"2026-03-23T04:36:55.808Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2424a9e7a45b4667b9388263","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"============================================================\r\n使用短期日期测试（最近30天）\r\n============================================================\r\n主板非ST股票: 3065\r\n\r\n测试股票: 000001 (平安银行)\r\n数据日期范围: 20260221 ~ 20260323（30天）\r\n错误: HTTPSConnectionPool(host='push2his.eastmoney.com', port=443): Max retries exceeded with url: /api/qt/stock/kline/get?fields1=f1%2Cf2%2Cf3%2Cf4%2Cf5%2Cf6&fields2=f51%2Cf52%2Cf53%2Cf54%2Cf55%2Cf56%2Cf57%2Cf58%2Cf59%2Cf60%2Cf61%2Cf116&ut=7eea3edcaed734bea9cbfc24409ed989&klt=101&fqt=1&secid=0.000001&beg=20260221&end=20260323 (Caused by ProxyError('Unable to connect to proxy', RemoteDisconnected('Remote end closed connection without response')))\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774240615794}}
{"type":"message","id":"b62f84fb","parentId":"3bd6a70b","timestamp":"2026-03-23T04:37:08.306Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题找到了！akshare尝试通过代理连接数据源，但代理无法连接。这是网络配置问题。\n\n这说明：\n1. akshare能够获取股票列表（5,491只）\n2. 但获取历史数据需要连接到东方财富的服务器（push2his.eastmoney.com）\n3. 由于代理问题导致连接失败\n\n解决方案：\n1. 不使用代理，直接连接\n2. 或者检查网络代理设置","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🔍 扫描失败原因已找到\n\n### 问题诊断\n\n**错误信息**：`ProxyError: Unable to connect to proxy`\n\n**原因分析**：\n- ✅ akshare能够获取股票列表（5,491只）\n- ✅ 能够筛选主板非ST股票（3,065只）\n- ❌ **获取历史数据失败**：akshare尝试通过代理连接东方财富服务器，但代理无法连接\n\n**影响**：\n- 无法获取股票历史数据（价格、成交量）\n- 无法计算技术指标（MA、RSI、成交量比）\n- 因此无法扫描出符合条件的候选股票\n\n---\n\n## 💡 解决方案\n\n### 方案1：禁用代理设置"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c5f045c218674467a7e2a786","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\n禁用代理的akshare测试\n\"\"\"\nimport os\nos.environ['NO_PROXY'] = '*'\nos.environ['no_proxy'] = '*'\nos.environ['HTTP_PROXY'] = ''\nos.environ['HTTPS_PROXY'] = ''\n\nprint(\"已禁用代理设置\")\n\nimport akshare as ak\n\ntry:\n    print(\"\\n开始测试获取历史数据...\")\n\n    from datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\n    # 测试获取最近30天数据\n    end_date = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n    start_date = (datetime.now() - timedelta(days=30)).strftime('%Y%m%d')\n\n    df = ak.stock_zh_a_hist(\n        symbol=\"000001\",\n        period=\"daily\",\n        start_date=start_date,\n        end_date=end_date,\n        adjust=\"qfq\"\n    )\n\n    print(f\"数据点数: {len(df)}\")\n\n    if len(df) > 0:\n        print(\"\\n最后5个交易日:\")\n        print(df[['日期', '收盘', '成交量']].tail())\n\n        # 计算指标\n        df['MA5'] = df['收盘'].rolling(window=5).mean()\n        df['MA10'] = df['收盘'].rolling(window=10).mean()\n\n        latest = df.iloc[-1]\n        prev = df.iloc[-2]\n\n        print(f\"\\nMA5: {latest['MA5']:.2f}\")\n        print(f\"MA10: {latest['MA10']:.2f}\")\n\n        golden = (prev['MA5'] < prev['MA10']) and (latest['MA5'] > latest['MA10'])\n        print(f\"金叉: {'是' if golden else '否'}\")\n\n    print(\"\\n✅ 测试成功！\")\n\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"错误: {e}\")\n","path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\no_proxy_test.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":261,"output":728,"cacheRead":124032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125021,"cost":{"input":0.00015659999999999998,"output":0.0016016000000000001,"cacheRead":0.013643520000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01540172}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774240615809}}
