/qqvoice>\"\n3. 支持格式: .silk, .slk, .slac, .amr, .wav, .mp3, .ogg, .pcm\n4. ⚠️ <qqvoice> 只用于语音文件，图片请用 <qqimg>；两者不要混用\n5. 可以同时发送文字和语音，系统会按顺序投递\n6. ⚠️ 插件 TTS 未配置: 如果你有 TTS 工具（如 audio_speech），仍可用它生成音频文件后用 <qqvoice> 发送；若无 TTS 工具，则无法主动生成语音\n7. 语音识别未配置（STT），无法自动转录用户的语音消息\n\n【发送文件 - 必须遵守】\n1. 发文件方法: 在回复文本中写 <qqfile>文件路径或URL</qqfile>，系统自动处理\n2. 示例: \"这是你要的文档 <qqfile>/tmp/report.pdf</qqfile>\"\n3. 支持: 本地文件路径、公网 URL\n4. 适用于非图片非语音的文件（如 pdf, docx, xlsx, zip, txt 等）\n5. ⚠️ 图片用 <qqimg>，语音用 <qqvoice>，其他文件用 <qqfile>\n\n【发送视频 - 必须遵守】\n1. 发视频方法: 在回复文本中写 <qqvideo>路径或URL</qqvideo>，系统自动处理\n2. 示例: \"<qqvideo>https://example.com/video.mp4</qqvideo>\" 或 \"<qqvideo>/path/to/video.mp4</qqvideo>\"\n3. 支持: 公网 URL、本地文件路径（系统自动读取上传）\n4. ⚠️ 视频用 <qqvideo>，图片用 <qqimg>，语音用 <qqvoice>，文件用 <qqfile>\n\n禁用代理设置"}],"timestamp":1774243838578}}
{"type":"message","id":"8abae90e","parentId":"5c2962e9","timestamp":"2026-03-23T05:31:10.288Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"禁用代理设置\"，这是为了解决之前遇到的 akshare 连接错误。\n\n之前的错误是：\n```\nProxyError: Unable to connect to proxy\n```\n\n这意味着 akshare 正在尝试通过代理连接到东方财富服务器，但代理连接失败。\n\n我需要：\n1. 确认当前代理状态\n2. 提供禁用代理的方法\n3. 提供替代数据源方案（因为 akshare 可能持续有问题）\n\n让我帮助用户禁用代理设置，并提供备选方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我来帮你禁用代理设置，解决 akshare 连接问题。\n\n## 🔧 方法1：在 Python 代码中禁用代理"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_70749777d6404f1bb55bd814","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"\n禁用代理的 akshare 测试\n\"\"\"\nimport os\n\n# 清除所有代理环境变量\nprint(\"禁用代理设置...\")\n\nos.environ['HTTP_PROXY'] = ''\nos.environ['HTTPS_PROXY'] = ''\nos.environ['http_proxy'] = ''\nos.environ['https_proxy'] = ''\nos.environ['NO_PROXY'] = '*'\n\nprint(\"代理设置已禁用\")\n\nimport akshare as ak\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\nprint(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*60)\nprint(\"测试 akshare 数据源（无代理）\")\nprint(\"=\"*60)\n\ntry:\n    # 获取主板股票\n    print(\"\\n[1] 获取主板非ST股票...\")\n    stocks = ak.stock_info_a_code_name()\n    main_board = stocks[\n        (stocks['code'].str.startswith('60') | stocks['code'].str.startswith('00'))\n    ]\n    non_st = main_board[\n        ~main_board['name'].str.contains('ST')\n    ]\n    print(f\"主板非ST股票：{len(non_st)}\")\n\n    # 获取历史数据测试（最近30天）\n    if len(non_st) > 0:\n        test_code = non_st.iloc[0]['code']\n        test_name = non_st.iloc[0]['name']\n\n        print(f\"\\n[2] 测试获取 {test_code}({test_name}) 历史数据...\")\n\n        end_date = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\n        start_date = (datetime.now() - timedelta(days=30)).strftime('%Y%m%d')\n\n        print(f\"日期范围: {start_date} ~ {end_date}\")\n\n        df = ak.stock_zh_a_hist(\n            symbol=test_code,\n            period=\"daily\",\n            start_date=start_date,\n            end_date=end_date,\n            adjust=\"qfq\"\n        )\n\n        print(f\"数据点数: {len(df)}\")\n        print(f\"数据列: {list(df.columns)}\")\n\n        if len(df) > 0:\n            # 计算技术指标\n            df['MA5'] = df['close'].rolling(window=5).mean()\n            df['MA10'] = df['close'].rolling(window=10).mean()\n            df['AvgVolume'] = df['volume'].rolling(window=20).mean()\n            df['VolumeRatio'] = df['volume'] / df['AvgVolume']\n\n            latest = df.iloc[-1]\n            prev = df.iloc[-2]\n\n            # 金叉检查\n            golden_cross = (prev['MA5'] < prev['MA10']) and (latest['MA5'] > latest['MA10'])\n\n            # 成交量检查\n            vol_ok = latest['VolumeRatio'] >= 1.5\n\n            # RSI计算\n            delta = df['close'].diff()\n            gain = (delta.where(delta > 0, 0)).rolling(window=14).mean()\n            loss = (-delta.where(delta < 0, 0)).rolling(window=14).mean()\n            rs = gain / loss\n            rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + rs))\n            latest_rsi = rsi.iloc[-1]\n\n            print(f\"\\n[3] 技术指标:\")\n            print(f\"收盘价: {latest['close']:.2f}\")\n            print(f\"MA5: {latest['MA5']:.2f}, MA10: {latest['MA10']:.2f}\")\n            print(f\"金叉: {'是' if golden_cross else '否'}\")\n            print(f\"成交量比: {latest['VolumeRatio']:.2f}\")\n            print(f\"RSI: {latest_rsi:.2f}\")\n\n            # 检查买入条件\n            print(f\"\\n[4] 检查买入条件:\")\n            print(f\"金叉条件: {'✅' if golden_cross else '❌'}\")\n            print(f\"成交量条件(≥1.5倍): {'✅' if vol_ok else '❌'} ({latest['VolumeRatio']:.2f})\")\n            rsi_ok = not pd.isna(latest_rsi) and latest_rsi < 70\n            print(f\"RSI条件(<70): {'✅' if rsi_ok else '❌'} ({latest_rsi:.2f})\")\n\n            all_ok = golden_cross and vol_ok and rsi_ok\n            print(f\"\\n是否满足全部条件: {'✅ 是' if all_ok else '❌ 否'}\")\n\n            if all_ok:\n                print(f\"\\n🎯 找到候选股票：{test_code} {test_name}\")\n                print(f\"买入信号: MA5金叉 + 放量 + RSI低\")\n            else:\n                print(f\"\\n❌ 不满足全部条件\")\n\n    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*60)\n    print(\"✅ 测试成功！akshare 数据源可用（无代理）\")\n    print(\"=\"*60)\n\n    # 保存配置建议\n    with open('proxy_config_recommendation.txt', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        f.write(\"代理配置建议\\n\")\n        f.write(\"=\"*60 + \"\\n\\n\")\n        f.write(\"问题：akshare 通过代理连接失败\\n\")\n        f.write(\"解决方案：\\n\\n\")\n        f.write(\"方案1：在系统环境变量中禁用代理\\n\")\n        f.write(\"  - 右键 计算机 → 属性 → 高级系统设置 → 环境变量\\n\")\n        f.write(\"  - 新建/编辑以下变量（值留空）:\\n\")\n        f.write(\"    - HTTP_PROXY\\n\")\n        f.write(\"    - HTTPS_PROXY\\n\")\n        f.write(\"    - http_proxy\\n\")\n        f.write(\"    - https_proxy\\n\")\n        f.write(\"    - NO_PROXY = *\\n\\n\")\n        f.write(\"方案2：在 Python 代码中禁用（本脚本已完成）\\n\\n\")\n        f.write(\"方案3：在网络设置中禁用系统代理\\n\")\n\n    print(\"\\n配置建议已保存到：proxy_config_recommendation.txt\")\n\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"\\n❌ 错误: {e}\")\n    import traceback\n    traceback.print_exc()\n","path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\test_no_proxy.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":137213,"output":1587,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138800,"cost":{"input":0.08232779999999999,"output":0.0034914,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0858192}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774243838588}}
