{"type":"message","id":"d26d783a","parentId":"18dfa662","timestamp":"2026-03-23T05:37:07.154Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"还在运行。让我等待一下...实际上让我直接创建一个解决方案脚本，不依赖akshare，使用tushare作为备用数据源，这样即使akshare有代理问题，系统也能工作。\n\n我应该提供一个综合的解决方案，包括：\n1. tushare版本的扫描脚本（备用方案）\n2. 手动输入股票数据的方案（如果在线数据源都不可用）\n\n这样用户就有多个选择。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_41fc9dc4000c4569b1101769","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"poll","sessionId":"25028","timeout":15000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":137213,"output":193,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137406,"cost":{"input":0.08232779999999999,"output":0.0004246,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.08275239999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774244203045}}
