{"type":"message","id":"b4dccf82","parentId":"4aed2574","timestamp":"2026-03-23T05:59:02.686Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"仍然是404错误。看来这个token有问题，或者token配置不正确。让我检查一下tushare的API调用方式。\n\n从错误信息看，tushare尝试访问了 `https://tushare.pro/document/2`，这说明可能是在请求某些文档API。\n\n问题可能在于：\n1. Token 不正确或无效\n2. Token 没有正确配置\n3. tushare版本问题\n\n让我创建一个更简单的测试脚本，直接测试token是否有效。\n\n另外，我也可以尝试使用其他方式，比如不使用pro_api，而是使用普通的接口。\n\n让我创建一个不依赖token的简化版本测试。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ⚠️ 404 错误持续：Token 可能无效\n\n错误显示 tushare API 返回 404，说明提供的 token 可能不正确或已过期。让我创建一个不依赖 token 的测试版本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a93e7dfca8fe4250bb85f2aa","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\nTushare test WITHOUT token (use public interface)\n\"\"\"\n\nprint(\"=\"*60)\nprint(\"Tushare Test - Public Interface (No Token Required)\")\nprint(\"=\"*60)\n\ntry:\n    import tushare as ts\n    from datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\n    # Use public interface (no token needed)\n    print(\"\\n[Test 1] Getting stock list (no token)...\")\n\n    # Get all A-shares\n    stocks = ts.get_stock_basics()\n    print(f\"Total stocks: {len(stocks)}\")\n\n    # Show first 5\n    print(\"\\nFirst 5 stocks:\")\n    print(stocks.head(5).to_string())\n\n    # Test getting main board stocks\n    print(\"\\n[Test 2] Filtering main board stocks (60/00)...\")\n\n    # Get stock list\n    stock_list = ts.get_stock_basics()\n\n    # Filter main board\n    main_board = stock_list[\n        (stock_list.index.str.startswith('60') | stock_list.index.str.startswith('00'))\n    ]\n    print(f\"Main board stocks: {len(main_board)}\")\n\n    # Exclude ST\n    non_st = main_board[~main_board.index.str.contains('ST')]\n    print(f\"Non-ST main board: {len(non_st)}\")\n\n    # Show first 10\n    print(\"\\nFirst 10 main board non-ST stocks:\")\n    print(non_st.head(10).to_string())\n\n    # Test getting historical data\n    if len(non_st) > 0:\n        test_code = non_st.index[0]\n        test_name = non_st.loc[test_code, 'name']\n\n        print(f\"\\n[Test 3] Getting history for {test_code}({test_name})...\")\n\n        end_date = datetime.now()\n        start_date = end_date - timedelta(days=30)\n\n        print(f\"Date range: {start_date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d')} ~ {end_date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d')}\")\n\n        df = ts.get_hist(\n            test_code,\n            start_date=start_date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d'),\n            end_date=end_date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d'),\n            ktype='D',\n            adjust='qfq'\n        )\n\n        print(f\"Data points: {len(df)}\")\n        print(f\"Columns: {list(df.columns)}\")\n\n        if len(df) > 0:\n            print(\"\\nLast 5 trading days:\")\n            print(df[['date', 'close', 'open', 'volume']].tail().to_string())\n\n            print(\"\\n[Test 4] Testing strategy indicators...\")\n\n            # Calculate MA5 and MA10\n            df['ma5'] = df['close'].rolling(window=5).mean()\n            df['ma10'] = df['close'].rolling(window=10).mean()\n\n            latest = df.iloc[-1]\n            prev = df.iloc[-2]\n\n            # Check golden cross\n            golden_cross = (prev['ma5'] < prev['ma10']) and (latest['ma5'] > latest['ma10'])\n\n            # Calculate volume ratio\n            avg_volume = df['volume'].iloc[-20:].mean()\n            vol_ratio = latest['volume'] / avg_volume\n\n            # Calculate RSI\n            delta = df['close'].diff()\n            gain = (delta.where(delta > 0, 0)).rolling(window=14).mean()\n            loss = (-delta.where(delta < 0, 0)).rolling(window=14).mean()\n            rs = gain / loss\n            rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + rs))\n            latest_rsi = rsi.iloc[-1]\n\n            print(f\"MA5: {latest['ma5']:.2f}, MA10: {latest['ma10']:.2f}\")\n            print(f\"Golden Cross: {'Yes' if golden_cross else 'No'}\")\n            print(f\"Volume Ratio: {vol_ratio:.2f}x (avg: {avg_volume:.0f})\")\n            print(f\"RSI: {latest_rsi:.2f}\")\n\n            # Check if meets buy conditions\n            print(\"\\n[Buy Signal Check]\")\n            print(f\"Golden Cross (MA5>MA10): {'OK' if golden_cross else 'FAIL'}\")\n            print(f\"Volume Ratio (>=1.5): {'OK' if vol_ratio >= 1.5 else 'FAIL'} ({vol_ratio:.2f})\")\n            print(f\"RSI (<70): {'OK' if latest_rsi < 70 else 'FAIL'} ({latest_rsi:.2f})\")\n\n            all_ok = golden_cross and (vol_ratio >= 1.5) and (latest_rsi < 70)\n            print(f\"\\nALL CONDITIONS: {'OK - BUY SIGNAL' if all_ok else 'FAIL'}\")\n\n            if all_ok:\n                print(f\"\\n>>> FOUND BUY SIGNAL: {test_code} {test_name}\")\n                print(f\"Price: {latest['close']:.2f}\")\n                print(f\"Signal: MA5({latest['ma5']:.2f}) > MA10({latest['ma10']:.2f}) + Vol({vol_ratio:.2f}x) + RSI({latest_rsi:.1f})\")\n\n    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*60)\n    print(\"Test Complete!\")\n    print(\"=\"*60)\n    print(\"\\n>> If test successful, tushare is working without token\")\n    print(\">> You can use the public interface for stock scanning\")\n\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"\\n[ERROR] {e}\")\n    import traceback\n    traceback.print_exc()\n","path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\test_tushare_public.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":137213,"output":1521,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138734,"cost":{"input":0.08232779999999999,"output":0.0033462,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.08567399999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774245502449}}
