/qqvoice>\"\n3. 支持格式: .silk, .slk, .slac, .amr, .wav, .mp3, .ogg, .pcm\n4. ⚠️ <qqvoice> 只用于语音文件，图片请用 <qqimg>；两者不要混用\n5. 可以同时发送文字和语音，系统会按顺序投递\n6. ⚠️ 插件 TTS 未配置: 如果你有 TTS 工具（如 audio_speech），仍可用它生成音频文件后用 <qqvoice> 发送；若无 TTS 工具，则无法主动生成语音\n7. 语音识别未配置（STT），无法自动转录用户的语音消息\n\n【发送文件 - 必须遵守】\n1. 发文件方法: 在回复文本中写 <qqfile>文件路径或URL</qqfile>，系统自动处理\n2. 示例: \"这是你要的文档 <qqfile>/tmp/report.pdf</qqfile>\"\n3. 支持: 本地文件路径、公网 URL\n4. 适用于非图片非语音的文件（如 pdf, docx, xlsx, zip, txt 等）\n5. ⚠️ 图片用 <qqimg>，语音用 <qqvoice>，其他文件用 <qqfile>\n\n【发送视频 - 必须遵守】\n1. 发视频方法: 在回复文本中写 <qqvideo>路径或URL</qqvideo>，系统自动处理\n2. 示例: \"<qqvideo>https://example.com/video.mp4</qqvideo>\" 或 \"<qqvideo>/path/to/video.mp4</qqvideo>\"\n3. 支持: 公网 URL、本地文件路径（系统自动读取上传）\n4. ⚠️ 视频用 <qqvideo>，图片用 <qqimg>，语音用 <qqvoice>，文件用 <qqfile>\n\n重新测试token"}],"timestamp":1774245885375}}
{"type":"message","id":"e65ceae8","parentId":"064bda7f","timestamp":"2026-03-23T06:05:24.352Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发了另一个看起来是十六进制的哈希值：`MV2pVNSHK-YgwemM2tBSt0LfpA1LQ7nPVta6xzNNjndPKqgS8GpOC0naj26896JawWLBnPsOL4m9jxp8NoXJm8s!`\n\n用户说\"重新测试token\"。\n\n我需要尝试用这个哈希值作为 tushare token 来测试连接。虽然看起来不太像正常的 token 格式（通常 tushare token 是 32 位十六进制字符串，但这个看起来有横杠），但我应该按照用户的要求，将这个值配置到脚本中并重新运行测试。\n\n让我更新脚本中的 token 为用户提供的这个值，然后运行测试。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我来用你提供的哈希值更新 tushare token 并重新测试："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_50c0a1ca54604afbb82e8658","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\nTushare token re-test using user-provided hash\n\"\"\"\n\nimport tushare as ts\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nimport sys\n\n# User-provided token hash\nTUSHARE_TOKEN = \"MV2pVNSHK-YgwemM2tBSt0LfpA1LQ7nPVta6xzNNjndPKqgS8GpOC0naj26896JawWLBnPsOL4m9jxp8NoXJm8s\"\n\nprint(\"User-provided token: MV2pVNSHK-YgwemM...\")\n\ntry:\n    # Test tushare connection with user token\n    print(\"\\n[1] Testing tushare connection with user token...\")\n\n    # Pro API with token\n    pro_api = ts.pro_api(token=TUSHARE_TOKEN)\n\n    print(\"[2] Getting stock list...\")\n    stocks = pro_api.stock_basic(\n        ts_code='',\n        fields=['code', 'name', 'list_date']\n    )\n\n    print(f\"Success! Got {len(stocks)} stocks\")\n\n    # Filter main board (60/00)\n    main_board = stocks[\n        (stocks['code'].str.startswith('60') | stocks['code'].str.startswith('00'))\n    ]\n\n    print(f\"Main board stocks: {len(main_board)}\")\n\n    # Exclude ST\n    non_st = main_board[\n        ~main_board['name'].str.contains('ST')\n    ]\n\n    print(f\"Non-ST main board: {len(non_st)}\")\n\n    # Show first 5\n    print(\"\\nFirst 5 non-ST main board stocks:\")\n    print(non_st.head(5).to_string())\n\n    # Test historical data\n    if len(non_st) > 0:\n        test_code = non_st.iloc[0]['code']\n        test_name = non_st.iloc[0]['name']\n\n        print(f\"\\n[3] Testing history for {test_code} ({test_name})...\")\n\n        end_date = datetime.now()\n        start_date = end_date - timedelta(days=30)\n\n        print(f\"Date range: {start_date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d')} ~ {end_date.strftime('%Y-%m-%d')}\")\n\n        df = ts.get_hist(\n            test_code,\n            start_date=start_date.strftime('%Y%m%d'),\n            end_date=end_date.strftime('%Y%m%d'),\n            ktype='D',\n            adjust='qfq'\n        )\n\n        print(f\"Data points: {len(df)}\")\n\n        if len(df) > 0:\n            # Calculate indicators\n            df['ma5'] = df['close'].rolling(window=5).mean()\n            df['ma10'] = df['close'].rolling(window=10).mean()\n            df['avg_volume'] = df['volume'].rolling(window=20).mean()\n            df['volume_ratio'] = df['volume'] / df['avg_volume']\n\n            latest = df.iloc[-1]\n            prev = df.iloc[-2]\n\n            print(f\"\\n[4] Technical indicators:\")\n            print(f\"MA5: {latest['ma5']:.2f}, MA10: {latest['ma10']:.2f}\")\n\n            golden = (prev['ma5'] < prev['ma10']) and (latest['ma5'] > latest['ma10'])\n            print(f\"Golden Cross (MA5>MA10): {'Yes' if golden else 'No'}\")\n\n            print(f\"Volume Ratio: {latest['volume_ratio']:.2f}\")\n\n            # Calculate RSI\n            delta = df['close'].diff()\n            gain = (delta.where(delta > 0, 0)).rolling(window=14).mean()\n            loss = (-delta.where(delta < 0, 0)).rolling(window=14).mean()\n            rs = gain / loss\n            rsi = 100 - (100 / (1 + rs))\n\n            print(f\"RSI: {rsi.iloc[-1]:.2f}\")\n\n            # Check buy conditions\n            print(f\"\\n[5] Buy Signal Check:\")\n\n            golden_ok = golden\n            vol_ok = latest['volume_ratio'] >= 1.5\n            rsi_ok = rsi.iloc[-1] < 70\n\n            print(f\"Golden Cross (MA5>MA10): {'OK' if golden_ok else 'FAIL'}\")\n            print(f\"Volume Ratio (>=1.5): {'OK' if vol_ok else 'FAIL'} ({latest['volume_ratio']:.2f})\")\n            print(f\"RSI (<70): {'OK' if rsi_ok else 'FAIL'} ({rsi.iloc[-1]:.2f})\")\n\n            all_ok = golden_ok and vol_ok and rsi_ok\n\n            print(f\"\\nAll Conditions Met: {'YES - BUY SIGNAL' if all_ok else 'NO'}\")\n\n            if all_ok:\n                print(f\"\\n>>> FOUND BUY SIGNAL: {test_code} {test_name}\")\n                print(f\"Price: {latest['close']:.2f}\")\n                print(f\"Signal: MA5({latest['ma5']:.2f}) > MA10({latest['ma10']:.2f}) + Volume({latest['volume_ratio']:.2f}x) + RSI({rsi.iloc[-1]:.1f})\")\n\n    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*60)\n    print(\"Token Test Complete!\")\n    print(\"=\"*60)\n    print(f\"\\nToken: {TUSHARE_TOKEN}\")\n    print(f\"Status: Working (if no errors above)\")\n    print(f\"\\nIf successful, tushare is working with this token!\")\n    print(f\"You can now run the main scanner.\")\n\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"\\n[ERROR] {e}\")\n    import traceback\n    traceback.print_exc()\n\nprint(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*60)\nprint(\"Token Re-Test Complete\")\nprint(\"=\"*60)\n","path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\test_token_rehash.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":137213,"output":1621,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138834,"cost":{"input":0.08232779999999999,"output":0.0035662000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.085894}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774245885383}}
