{"type":"message","id":"e383770b","parentId":"e282e72b","timestamp":"2026-03-23T06:07:40.860Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"tushare 已经是最新版本（1.4.25）。版本不是问题。\n\n问题可能出在：\n1. Token 格式不对\n2. Token 已过期或失效\n3. API 方法调用有变化\n\n既然用户能访问 https://tushare.pro/，让我创建一个更简单的测试脚本，使用更基础的方法：\n- 使用 ts.pro_bar 而不是 ts.pro_api\n- 或者直接用最简单的方法调用\n\n我还可以创建一个完全手动的版本，用户可以手动输入股票代码和价格来模拟交易。\n\n或者，我可以尝试使用不同的 API 端点：\n- ts.pro_api 的不同方法\n- 或者使用 ts.bar 接口\n\n让我创建一个更简单的测试脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"tushare 版本已是最新的。问题可能是 API 调用方式。让我创建一个更简单的测试脚本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_83f4b0c7b8f0460b81f3de6b","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\nSimple Tushare Test - Multiple Methods\n\"\"\"\n\nprint(\"=\"*60)\nprint(\"Testing Multiple Tushare Connection Methods\")\nprint(\"=\"*60)\n\n# Method 1: Using ts.pro (pro bar interface)\nprint(\"\\n[Method 1] Using ts.pro()...\")\ntry:\n    import tushare as ts\n\n    # Test 1a: Get stock list\n    print(\"[1a] Getting stock list...\")\n    stocks = ts.get_stock_basics()\n    print(f\"Success! Got {len(stocks)} stocks\")\n\n    # Test 1b: Filter main board\n    main_board = stocks[\n        (stocks.index.str.startswith('60') | stocks.index.str.startswith('00'))\n    ]\n    print(f\"Main board: {len(main_board)}\")\n\n    # Test 1c: Get history for first stock\n    if len(main_board) > 0:\n        test_code = main_board.index[0]\n        test_name = main_board.loc[test_code, 'name']\n\n        print(f\"[1b] Testing {test_code}({test_name}) history...\")\n\n        from datetime import datetime, timedelta\n        end_date = datetime.now()\n        start_date = end_date - timedelta(days=30)\n\n        df = ts.get_hist(\n            test_code,\n            start_date=start_date.strftime('%Y%m%d'),\n            end_date=end_date.strftime('%Y%m%d'),\n            ktype='D',\n            adjust='qfq'\n        )\n\n        print(f\"Data points: {len(df)}\")\n\n        if len(df) > 0:\n            print(\"\\nLast 3 trading days:\")\n            print(df[['date', 'close', 'open', 'volume']].tail(3).to_string())\n\n            # Calculate MA5 and MA10\n            df['ma5'] = df['close'].rolling(window=5).mean()\n            df['ma10'] = df['close'].rolling(window=10).mean()\n\n            latest = df.iloc[-1]\n            print(f\"\\nLatest close: {latest['close']:.2f}\")\n            print(f\"MA5: {latest['ma5']:.2f}\")\n            print(f\"MA10: {latest['ma10']:.2f}\")\n\n            golden = (df['ma5'].iloc[-2] < df['ma10'].iloc[-2]) and (latest['ma5'] > latest['ma10'])\n            print(f\"Golden Cross: {'Yes' if golden else 'No'}\")\n\n        print(\"\\n[Method 1] SUCCESS!\")\n\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"\\n[Method 1] FAILED: {e}\")\n\n# Method 2: Using ts.pro_api without token (free interface)\nprint(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*60)\nprint(\"[Method 2] Using ts.pro_api() (no token)...\")\ntry:\n    import tushare as ts\n\n    pro_api = ts.pro_api()\n\n    print(\"[2a] Getting stock list...\")\n    stocks = pro_api.stock_basic(\n        ts_code='',\n        fields=['code', 'name', 'list_date']\n    )\n\n    print(f\"Success! Got {len(stocks)} stocks\")\n\n    # Show first 5\n    print(\"\\nFirst 5 stocks:\")\n    print(stocks.head(5).to_string())\n\n    print(\"\\n[Method 2] SUCCESS!\")\n\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"\\n[Method 2] FAILED: {e}\")\n\n# Method 3: Testing specific stock\nprint(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*60)\nprint(\"[Method 3] Testing specific stock (600000 Pudong Bank)...\")\ntry:\n    import tushare as ts\n    from datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\n    # Get history for 600000\n    end_date = datetime.now()\n    start_date = end_date - timedelta(days=30)\n\n    df = ts.get_hist(\n        '600000',\n        start_date=start_date.strftime('%Y%m%d'),\n        end_date=end_date.strftime('%Y%m%d'),\n        ktype='D',\n        adjust='qfq'\n    )\n\n    print(f\"Data points: {len(df)}\")\n    print(f\"Columns: {list(df.columns)}\")\n\n    if len(df) > 0:\n        print(\"\\nLast 3 days:\")\n        print(df[['date', 'close', 'open', 'volume']].tail(3).to_string())\n\n        # Calculate indicators\n        df['ma5'] = df['close'].rolling(window=5).mean()\n        df['ma10'] = df['close'].rolling(window=10).mean()\n\n        latest = df.iloc[-1]\n        print(f\"\\nMA5: {latest['ma5']:.2f}\")\n        print(f\"MA10: {latest['ma10']:.2f}\")\n\n        golden = (df['ma5'].iloc[-2] < df['ma10'].iloc[-2]) and (latest['ma5'] > latest['ma10'])\n        print(f\"Golden Cross: {'Yes' if golden else 'No'}\")\n\n        print(\"\\n[Method 3] SUCCESS!\")\n\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"\\n[Method 3] FAILED: {e}\")\n\nprint(\"\\n\" + \"=\"*60)\nprint(\"Test Complete!\")\nprint(\"=\"*60)\nprint(\"\\n>> If any method succeeded, we can update the scanner to use that method\")\nprint(\">> If all methods failed, there may be a network or firewall issue blocking Python requests\")\nprint(\">> But since you can access https://tushare.pro/ in browser, Python should work too\")\n","path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\test_tushare_all_methods.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":137213,"output":1517,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138730,"cost":{"input":0.08232779999999999,"output":0.0033374000000000003,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0856652}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774246019331}}
